	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">WoW: LARGE Client Patch, March 22, 2005</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Kevin "Nocte" Dolley</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Mar 22, 2005, 22:32</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=WoW%3A%20LARGE%20Client%20Patch%2C%20March%2022%2C%202005&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Fnews%2FWoW%2Fnews_35.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
